Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane! Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Kunad Highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This was what we woke up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can remember was the earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that thing caused by an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity around that thing is abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't contact Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka and Yuito are nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Yuito too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If Karen really betrays us all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,something might unfold in Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's return to Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A TOMORROW OF RUIN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Suoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole city is non-operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Arahabaki still in operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder we couldn't\Nget in touch with Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this is the research facility of my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean Spring Pharmaceuticals?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But as I remembered, we had no\Nresearch facility in Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this place really the Suoh we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is amiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It bears the marking of Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks very similar to that ampoule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's hope after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Major General Karen's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a skill of SS class, Brain Eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He can copy another person's power\Nand use it as his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would he copy Kasane's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He can already use psychokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We must find out what happened to Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,People with powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even while facing the end of the world,\Nyou still chose to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito Sumeragi, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really Yuito Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the voice, you must be Kyoka Eden\Nand Shiden Ritter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know what happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but Yuito Sumeragi, you've lost your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-I am...\N-Arashi Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognize the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to be in\NSuoh capital of the year 2020.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But this place doesn't seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Suoh of the year 2070.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 2070? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, only people\Nwith the power to time travel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,can stay in a different timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Time travel power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those caught up in the turbulence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,will be sent back to their original timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power isn't psychokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power to manipulate gravity and\Ndimension, making it seem like psychokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the power to travel through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the wielder of Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those scarlet strings were the power\Nto travel through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Arahabaki told me you would come from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Until just now, I was doubting its prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After Karen joined hands with Seiran\Nto launch a rebellion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka wanted to defend its pride\Nas a powerful nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They put a man named\NYuito Sumeragi on a pedestal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to distract the people's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"PRIME SUSPECT: KASANE RANDALL"\NKasane, you became the prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed the Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The conflict between Suoh and Seiran escalated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was battling the Others,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also fighting against\Nthe power users from Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's gained more influence\Nwithout me noticing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I created this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that looks like a black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We created it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Our powers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,share the same property of manipulating gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I have the ability\Nto travel through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am also a wielder of Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our powers resonated
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave birth to the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't travel through time on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-That was...\N-The Kunad Gate is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's slowly consuming the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, the Gate will appear after\Na successful time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It should disappear right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But because my power was resonating to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the Gate remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, every time I use my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the Gate will alter the space around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It consumes the world around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no way to stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My power is sustaining the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I die, the Gate will be gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only way to get rid of the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't choose that path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those around me persuaded me\Nthat there were other ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But the more I searched,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the more I realized my death was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gate is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's growing because I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, please kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you for a favor.\NI need you to take my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the Kunad Gate has expanded,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you must eliminate the false hero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you know as Yuito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure if I could go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Strings can be triggered by\Nemotional fluctuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens when the heart suffers great trauma
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or a belief wavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The government ordered Suoh to carry on\Nwith the experiment to turn people into Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, the Suoh forces tried to\Nturn the Seiran Garrison soldiers into Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was the person who ordered\Nthe experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after being sung as a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,even after I had learned the truth,\NI didn't stop the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You let them carry on with the experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They turned most of the people into Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like what they did to Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The research on power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,was a search for immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, what have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for the sake of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I back to my timeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi told me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Suoh capital is in total chaos\Nbecause of the uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can hear me, please regroup with us\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The rendezvous point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka? Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,An uprising at Suoh capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and the team are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I die, the Gate will be gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They turned most of the people into Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like what they did to Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The future with Yuito in it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer accessible\Nbecause of my time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can create a new future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Kunad Gate didn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the whole world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Blind citizens of New Himuka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the foolish people who chose\Nto ignore the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Karen Travers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've awakened after I opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the government's conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My comrades and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Karen, what are you planning?\N-have joined hands with Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Some agile variants show up\Nfrom time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I should keep an eye out for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A shelter for the officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate is wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi. Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The OSF...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Togetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your strength. I'll get the medics here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me be, go to a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the organization that turned\NNaomi Randall into an Other
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the New Himuka Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yuito from the future was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for the sake of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done to my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This knife... Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to retreat right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yuito...\N-Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware of this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a close call\Nwith all those people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you fighting Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on Karen's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that why you killed Chairman Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I could ask you the same thing.\NWhy were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to rescue the council members.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But sadly, I was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, sorry for breaking off just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've regrouped with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our current location is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We were already back in this world\Nbefore we even noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll explain it another time, Kagero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But what happened afterward, Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Strings and Kunad Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans were turned into Others?\NAnd Naomi too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to kill Yuito to save the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beyond ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the future Yuito told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Sumeragi was assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become their prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really going to take out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that privileged kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It took long enough to find you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The repair of Arahabaki is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The rebels have retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kasane Randall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know where she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keep searching for her.\N-Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This knife... Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Personality rehabilitation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is a widely known secret of the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The stories are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,were born to be the government\Nand the country's cattle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My father and brother knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware of this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Tsugumi's clairvoyance,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we've found Kyoka Platoon's rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero is with them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Around half of the OSF members
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have sided with Major General Karen\Nand joined hands with the Seiran Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are rumors Seiran\Nwill declare its independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Psynet is back online.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, Haruka is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's left as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She is always worried about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal she's worried\Nabout Kasane and the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the headquarters at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you to be the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going\Nin your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,TRACKING DOWN NAGI
